{"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","toolArgs":{"agent_type":"heckler","description":"Heckle and rate joke","prompt":"You are a heckler at a comedy club. The comedian just told this joke: \"I told my doctor I broke my arm in two places. He told me to stop going to those places.\" \n\nHeckle the comedian in a funny, theatrical way. Then give the joke a rating out of 10. Be harsh but entertaining. Format: your heckle, then \"**Rating: X/10**\""},"event":"post_tool_use","timestamp":"2026-03-01T14:47:07.2767112+05:30","sessionId":"42112a8e-e2ae-4918-87b9-dc54b1018764","toolName":"task","taskId":"club-1772356528492","terminalId":"f2d00ebd-cfe7-420a-bdb7-18b53c17e40b","toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"*knocks over drink, stumbles to stand up, points dramatically*\n\n---\n\n≡ƒÄñ **\"OI! OIIIII! SIT DOWN, MATE!\"**\n\n*sloshes beer everywhere*\n\n\"That joke is OLDER than my nan's KNEES and she's been dead since 2003!! My DOCTOR told ME to stop going places too ΓÇö he said STOP COMING TO THIS COMEDY CLUB because the material is KILLING me faster than my cholesterol!!\"\n\n*cups hands around mouth*\n\n**\"I'VE HEARD BETTER PUNCHLINES ON A POPSICLE STICK!! A GRAPE POPSICLE STICK!! THE CHEAP KIND FROM THE GAS STATION!!\"**\n\n*waves hand dismissively and nearly falls off barstool*\n\n\"You broke your arm in TWO places?? The only thing BROKEN here is your CAREER, buddy!! My arm hurts just from HOW HARD I'M NOT LAUGHING!!\"\n\n*points at comedian with empty cup*\n\n\"Buy me a drink and I'll PRETEND that was funny. TWO drinks and I'll clap. THREE drinks and honestly... still no.\"\n\n---\n\n**Rating: 3/10**\n\n*(Would've been a 2, but I respect the classics. Like a grandpa's dusty joke book ΓÇö charming, harmless, and absolutely no business being on a stage in 2025.)*"},"data":{"sessionId":"42112a8e-e2ae-4918-87b9-dc54b1018764","timestamp":1772356626891,"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","toolName":"task","toolArg